---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-8">About CineReview</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Welcome to CineReview, your trusted source for thoughtful, honest movie reviews.
        We believe that great cinema deserves more than a simple thumbs up or down.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        In a world of endless streaming options and countless new releases,
        finding movies worth your time can be overwhelming. That's where we come in.
        Our mission is to help you discover films that will truly move, entertain,
        and inspire you.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p>
        We don't just rate moviesâ€”we explore them. Each review dives into the
        storytelling, performances, cinematography, and what makes a film tick.
        Whether it's a blockbuster or an indie gem, we approach every movie
        with the same level of care and analysis.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Rating System</h2>
      <p>
        We use a 10-point scale that accounts for all aspects of filmmaking:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>9-10:</strong> Masterpiece - A must-watch that will stay with you</li>
        <li><strong>7-8:</strong> Great - Highly recommended with minor flaws</li>
        <li><strong>5-6:</strong> Good - Worth watching if you enjoy the genre</li>
        <li><strong>3-4:</strong> Below Average - Some redeeming qualities</li>
        <li><strong>1-2:</strong> Skip It - Not worth your time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>
        We love hearing from fellow movie enthusiasts! Feel free to leave comments
        on our reviews, share your own ratings, and save your favorites.
        Cinema is best enjoyed as a community.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-dark-card rounded-xl border border-dark-border">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-4">Get in Touch</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
        Have a movie you'd like us to review? Questions or feedback?
        We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@cinereview.com"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 transition"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
        </svg>
        hello@cinereview.com
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
